data.description: NEW CARPET and PRICED TO SELL! This home has SOLAR PANELS to help LOWER those HIGH ELECTRIC BILLS! The fridge, washer and dryer come with your new home.  You know what "everyone" and the "experts" are saying.  They are screaming mayhem in the streets, creating panic, telling anyone who will listen, that "interest rates are too high!"  Sadly, you know the uninformed will believe the "gurus" distortion of historical facts about interest rates.  You know pessimistic homebuyers will miss their opportunity to WIN BIG in the current market.  And I know you're smarter than the rest of the crowd.  I know you can see through the artificial hype and smoke screens designed to generate internet clicks.  I know you realize NOW is the time to have courage and take ACTION when a Golden Opportunity comes your way. This is your opportunity to buy a wonderful home at a BARGAIN price and move in just before the holidays. Your new home is located in the quiet and gated Pointe section of the Wortham Oaks subdivision.  This clean, open floor plan home has high ceilings, NEW CARPET, neutral colors and is ready for you to move in. Enter your new home and to the left you will find a flex area that can serve as an office or extra bedroom. Continue through the home and imagine yourself at the large kitchen island spending quality time with the ones you love. The kitchen has granite counters, stainless steel appliances and gas cooking.  Let's keep cruising through your new home and check out the primary bedroom.  The primary bedroom is spacious and has plenty of storage space with TWO separate closets. The primary bathroom features dual vanity sinks along with a separate shower and garden tub.  Make your way back to the middle of your new home and you will find the secondary bedrooms that can accommodate a variety of different sized furniture. Head out the back door to enjoy peaceful moments protected by the screened in patio that keeps out natures winged intruders. Your neighbors suffer and have their patio time ruined.  Ahh, but not you my friend!  You have protection from those pesky oversized flying critters.  Everyone will label you an Ivy League genius for buying this home because it has a screened in patio.  Speaking of screened in, the garage has a neat feature that helps keep away the Texas flying dinosaur bugs.  The garage has a screen that allows the garage door to stay up which helps prevent those freeloading, non rent paying, flying bugs from becoming squatters in your garage!  Other features of this home are: smart thermostat, high quality water softener and an in ground sprinkler system. Your new home is a short drive to Loop 1604 that has plenty of shopping, dining and entertainment options. Curious if this will be your new home?  Of course you are! Don't miss your chance! Immediate, same day appointments are available.  I guarantee someone else has read this and is curious just like you.  The difference between you and them is they have already scheduled their appointment.  How would you feel if you waited all this time for the right home and missed out because someone else took action before you did?  Take MASSIVE ACTION and schedule your appointment now.
